OL,3,CClosing Torquay custody centre would
OL,4,Chit 'most vulnerable', say lawyers
OL,6,FDefence solicitor Nigel Butts explains
OL,7,Fwhy he is concerned about the future
OL,8,Fof Torquay's custody centre
OL,10,FThe Chief Constable of Devon and
OL,11,FCornwall Police has said he is
OL,12,F'carefully considering' proposals to
OL,13,Fclose a custody centre at Torquay
OL,14,Fpolice station.
