OL,3,CClosing Torquay custody centre would
OL,4,Chit 'most vulnerable', say lawyers
OL,6,FJames Vaughan says the force must
OL,7,F'urgently improve' how it looks after
OL,8,Fdetainees across the region, adding
OL,9,Fthat the state of some cell blocks are
OL,10,Fnot currently meeting safety
OL,11,Fstandards, and present a welfare risk
OL,12,Fto staff and prisoners.
OL,14,FBut a group of lawyers and solicitors
OL,15,Fhave expressed concern and urged the
OL,16,Fforce to reconsider, saying closing
OL,17,Fthe centre would have a 'real world
OL,18,Fimpact on the most vulnerable.'
