OL,3,CClosing Torquay custody centre would
OL,4,Chit 'most vulnerable', say lawyers
OL,6,FDefence solicitor Nigel Butt said:
OL,7,F"Torquay custody centre is one of the
OL,8,Fbusiest in the region.
OL,10,F"It serves a large population across
OL,11,FTorbay, Teignbridge and South Devon,
OL,12,Fand plays a vital role in keeping
OL,13,Flocal policing efficient and
OL,14,Faccessible.
OL,16,F"On many evenings, there are only
OL,17,Faround eight response officers
OL,18,Fcovering the entire Torbay area.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
