OL,3,CClosing Torquay custody centre would
OL,4,Chit 'most vulnerable', say lawyers
OL,6,F"A single incident involving several
OL,7,Farrests ` which is not uncommon on
OL,8,Fbusy summer nights ` could take up
OL,9,Fmost, if not all, of those officers.
OL,11,F"If they have to transport detainees
OL,12,Fto Exeter, there would effectively be
OL,13,Fno officers left to respond to other
OL,14,Fserious incidents. Victims of crime
OL,15,Fcould be left waiting for help in a
OL,16,Fperilous situation."
