OL,3,CClosing Torquay custody centre would
OL,4,Chit 'most vulnerable', say lawyers
OL,6,FChief Constable James Vaughan said: "I
OL,7,Fhave commissioned a programme of work
OL,8,Fto review the force custody estate to
OL,9,Fexplore how improvements can be made
OL,10,Fto secure consistency of custody
OL,11,Fservices, strengthen detainee safety
OL,12,Fand control costs.
OL,26,@nD@eOU
