OL,3,CClosing Torquay custody centre would
OL,4,Chit 'most vulnerable', say lawyers
OL,6,F"Providers of healthcare, legal advice
OL,7,Fand appropriate adult services also
OL,8,Freport difficulties in maintaining
OL,9,Fconsistent services across all six
OL,10,Fcentres."
OL,12,FPolice and Crime Commissioner Alison
OL,13,FHernandez said any change 'must result
OL,14,Fin improvements to the safety of
OL,15,Fdetainees and an increase in the
OL,16,Fwellbeing and performance of staff and
OL,17,Fofficers.'
