OL,3,CClosing Torquay custody centre would
OL,4,Chit 'most vulnerable', say lawyers
OL,6,FSteve Darling, Liberal Democrat MP for
OL,7,FTorbay, said: "We don't know for
OL,8,Fcertain whether this closure is going
OL,9,Fahead. I am really concerned that this
OL,10,Fwill drag away officers - to Exeter if
OL,11,Fwe're lucky, worse still to Plymouth
OL,12,Fbecause Exeter's often full.
OL,14,F"Those officers will have to process
OL,15,Fcriminals there which will take them
OL,16,Foff the beat in Torbay which is
OL,17,Fabsolutely horrendous."
